snippet.description:
Island of Despair is a 9-level episode in the style of vanilla Heretic, intended for single-player, co-op and deathmatch.

► Download: https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/150210-heretic-island-of-despair/

► Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/iyagoep

► Donations: https://streamelements.com/iyagoep/tip

►Special thanks to:

@GrizzlyRed  for making the trailer
@borogk  for the Cameraman mod
@lukejansen3540  for the "The Cathedral" Remix
@RavenSoftware  for this amazing game

